abstract: Monsanto reports third-quarter profit of $2.39 a share, compared with $1.62 a share in year-ago quarter.
lead_paragraph: Monsanto reported better-than-expected earnings results for the third quarter on Wednesday as executives continued to make a case for a $45 billion takeover of Syngenta, a Swiss competitor.

headline.main: Monsanto Quarterly Earnings Outdo Analysts’ Expectations
